{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/1_ENG.gif?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/Plot_ENG.jpg?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The descent into horror begins...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You come to your senses in an unknown place. Everything around seems familiar, but memories slip away like sand through your fingers. The only thing left is to move forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/2.gif?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An inner voice tells you: <strong>you are a famous writer, the \u201cking of horror,\u201d whose stories made readers shudder with fear. </strong>But now reality is much more frightening than the worst nightmares that came from your pen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/3.gif?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What kind of place is this? Who's playing with your mind? Each discovery brings you closer to the solution, but at the same time opens the door to even more sinister depths. Time loses its meaning, and the line between fiction and reality blurs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Are you ready to face your own fears?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/4.gif?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/Gameplay_ENG.jpg?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Carefully examine</strong> everything around you; details play a crucial role in uncovering what happened here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve <strong>simple</strong> <strong>puzzles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/5.gif?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Beware of the monster</strong>; it is always somewhere nearby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Use the camera</strong> as a tool for solving puzzles \u2014 it will reveal what is hidden from the eye.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/6.gif?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/GameFeatures_ENG.jpg?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1. The game has autosave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2. Realistic graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3. High-quality sound design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4. Simple but interesting puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5. Average game completion time: 30-60 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6. Genre: Walking Simulator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/Attention_ENG.jpg?t=1738693185\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features machine translation into the following languages:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- French</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- German</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Spanish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Portuguese (Brazilian)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Chinese (Simplified)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Korean</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Polish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Japanese</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hello!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic